<section class="section"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Operating method</p><h2>Diagnose, map, prototype, harden.</h2><div class="workflow-band"><article class="process-step"><h3>Systems audit</h3><p>We find repeatable work, failure points, data owners, and decision moments.</p></article><article class="process-step"><h3>Command map</h3><p>Workflows become visual routes with inputs, rules, outputs, and review states.</p></article><article class="process-step"><h3>Prototype sprint</h3><p>A narrow version ships fast so teams can test the real operating rhythm.</p></article><article class="process-step"><h3>Release support</h3><p>Documentation, monitoring notes, and change control keep the system stable.</p></article></div></div></section>